verbose_text: Yet the data supporting this causation were limited as hPL has both insulin and anti-insulin effects and may actually be more important to stimulate the growth of maternal pancreatic islets and increase lipolysis and free fatty acid (FFA) liberation from adipocytes as an energy substrate.
